---
id: turkey-avocado-wrap
title: Turkey Avocado Wrap
description: A quick no-cook lunch wrap with turkey, avocado, and crisp vegetables.
servings: 2
mealTypes: [lunch]
tags: [quick, no-cook]
prep time: 10 minutes
cook time: 0 minutes
---

Spread @Greek yogurt{2%tbsp} on @large flour tortillas{2}.

Add @sliced turkey{6%oz}, @avocado{1}(sliced), @romaine lettuce{1%cup}, and @tomato{1}(sliced).

Roll tightly and slice in half with a #knife{}.
